<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-20417] When bootstrap fails the retry field is not populated which leads to a NPE</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-20417</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This was found while looking into ShortAccordSimulationTest failing seed 0xc0e3fe9c6cdedf29.  The error in CI just says repair failed but when you run this seed you see the following&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
ERROR [AccordExecutor[1,9]:1] node3 2025-03-06 09:07:46,873 AccordAgent.java:145 - Uncaught accord exception
java.lang.NullPointerException: &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
	at org.apache.cassandra.service.accord.api.AccordAgent.onFailedBootstrap(AccordAgent.java:133)
	at accord.local.Bootstrap$Attempt.fail(Bootstrap.java:274)
	at accord.coordinate.FetchCoordinator.exhausted(FetchCoordinator.java:213)
	at accord.coordinate.FetchCoordinator.trySendMore(FetchCoordinator.java:201)
	at accord.coordinate.FetchCoordinator.unavailable(FetchCoordinator.java:303)
	at accord.coordinate.FetchCoordinator.fail(FetchCoordinator.java:313)
	at org.apache.cassandra.service.accord.AccordFetchCoordinator.access$100(AccordFetchCoordinator.java:81)
	at org.apache.cassandra.service.accord.AccordFetchCoordinator$IncomingStream.lambda$maybeListen$0(AccordFetchCoordinator.java:210)
	at org.apache.cassandra.utils.concurrent.ListenerList$CallbackBiConsumerListener.run(ListenerList.java:268)
	at org.apache.cassandra.service.accord.AccordExecutor$PlainRunnable.run(AccordExecutor.java:1074)
	at org.apache.cassandra.service.accord.AccordExecutor$CommandStoreQueueTask.run(AccordExecutor.java:757)
	at org.apache.cassandra.service.accord.AccordExecutorAbstractLockLoop.runWithoutLock(AccordExecutorAbstractLockLoop.java:249)
	at org.apache.cassandra.concurrent.InfiniteLoopExecutor.loop(InfiniteLoopExecutor.java:125)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The reason for this is that org.apache.cassandra.service.accord.api.AccordWaitStrategies#retryBootstrap is never populated&lt;/p&gt;</description>
